author: Alec Leach
title: What London’s Streetwear Youths Wore to the Launch of Palace SS17 Drop 2
text:
Visit the original post to see all 15 images from this gallery. 
Location: London, UK
Season: Spring/Summer 2017
Key Looks: No surprises here — London’s youths turned up to the second drop of Palace SS17 decked out head-to-toe in streetwear. Personal faves include that flag-adorned Supreme hoodie (#1), some mental embroidered trousers (#3) and some faux Gucci goodness courtesy of Stussy (#4).
Editor’s Notes: Another day, another batch of coveted streetwear is released in the British capital. The UK’s style-conscious youths hit up Palace’s London store in the city’s bustling Soho district to get their hands on the latest gear from the skate juggernaut. See below for a video account of the day’s antics.

For more streetwear news, take a closer look at the United Arrows x adidas NMD City Sock sneaker .
